shortcuts.name: shortcuts
shortcuts.docstring:
This module collects helper functions and classes that "span" multiple levels
of MVC. In other words, these functions/classes introduce controlled coupling
for convenience's sake.

__main__.name: __main__
__main__.docstring:
Invokes django-admin when the django module is run as a script.

Example: python -m django check

__init__.name: dispatch.__init__
__init__.docstring:
Multi-consumer multi-producer dispatching mechanism

Originally based on pydispatch (BSD)
https://pypi.org/project/PyDispatcher/2.0.1/
See license.txt for original license.

Heavily modified for Django's purposes.

locmem.name: template.loaders.locmem
locmem.docstring: Wrapper for loading templates from a plain Python dict.

datastructures.docstring:
Useful auxiliary data structures for query construction. Not useful outside
the SQL domain.
